Package: MRBMM
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Mixture Model for Mendelian Randomization
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2026-01-28
Authors@R: c(
    person("Wang", "Yinwei", 
           email = "b627926373@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0474-9257"))
    )
Description: Implements a robust Bayesian mixture model for Mendelian 
    randomization that explicitly models horizontal pleiotropy. Supports 
    both 3-component and 4-component models with automatic model selection 
    via LOO-CV. Includes Weighted Mode initialization (Hartwig et al. 2017) 
    and comprehensive GWAS data harmonization with local plink.
